headline: Alphabet Stock Surges After Berkshire Hathaway Reveals Stake
summary: Alphabet shares gained 5.5% Monday morning after Warren Buffett's Berkshire Hathaway said it took a stake in Google's parent company.  Class-A shares recently changed hands at $291.83, on course to test new highs.
